🗓 Date: March 6, 2026
⏰ Time: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM
📍 Venue: Auditorium, GCE, Erode

🌐 Website: www.gustogcee.in

Technical Events

• Paper Presentation
• Project Presentation
• Prompt X
• Think Like a Compiler
• Code Chaos

Non-Technical Events

• Meme Contest
• Photography
• Short Film
• Icon IQ

🏆 Rewards: Medals, Cash Prizes &amp; Certificates

💰 Registration Fee: ₹250 per participant
✔ Participants can choose a maximum of 3 events (any combination)
🍽 Refreshments and lunch will be provided

For further details:
